-right\">ROUND BALL HEADS - ToolTreaux 12pc diamond burr set features round ball-shaped heads ideal for making concave cuts, engraving and hollowing out materials. The round-bottom tip slots and grooves make clean and rounded side cuts\nservice life</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">ASSORTED SIZES - Set comes with 12 different assorted head sizes. All burrs are designed to be compatible with stone, glass, tile, wood, plastic, fiberglass, ceramics and all-natural materials; great for hobby and crafting projects</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">150 GRIT (FINE) - Each diamond burr has a fine 150 grit to achieve a higher polish and finish than coarser grits more suited for heavy material removal. Burrs are made of high-quality stainless steel that won’t rust</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">STORAGE CASE INCLUDED - Burr set comes with heavy duty plastic carrying case with slots for each burr to keep them organized and stable when not in use. Small case easily fits inside most tool bags, boxes, pockets or craft storage organizers.</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">SPECIFICATIONS - 12pc set; Materials: stainless steel, plastic; Color: chrome; Grit: 150 (fine); Ball head shape: round; Sizes included: Assorted; Compatible with these materials: glass, tile, wood, fiberglass, ceramics and stone</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  </table>\n\t\t\t  </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t  </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t  <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t  <p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t  </div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t      </div> <!-- /container -->\n              <div style=\"clear:both\">\n    